{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118010/extras/GMGIF01.gif?t=1734015793\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After surviving a mysterious forest attack that erased his memory twelve years ago, a former Man in Black, now a field guide named Robert, leads a group of tourists to the source of an Alaskan river...  When they are attacked by the Grizzly Man, a mysterious and deadly figure linked to the CIA and Project MKUltra.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Will they survive? </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Or will they become the catch of the day?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118010/extras/GMGIF03.gif?t=1734015793\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Immerse yourself in the story with its rich, branching narratives and evocative illustrations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Decide the fate of characters in \u2018Choose Your Own Adventure\u2019 style gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Accessible, brain-tickling puzzles throughout the story\u2026 including a new variant of solitaire!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118010/extras/GMGIF04.gif?t=1734015793\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A Pixel Pulp slasher!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Grizzly Man</i></strong> is a standalone experience and the newest installment in the Pixel Pulps series of interactive adventures. Created by novelist Nico Saraintaris and artist Fernando Martinez Ruppel, Pixel Pulps fuse exceptional writing and stunning illustration, inspired by mid-20th century pulp fiction and 80s home computer graphics. Previous titles include <i>Mothmen 1966</i>, <i>Varney Lake</i>, and <i>Bahnsen Knights</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118010/extras/GMGIF02.gif?t=1734015793\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Grizzly Man</i>, like all the Pixel Pulps, is made to be played by anyone who enjoys fine storytelling.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"KNUCKLE MASTER!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3118010/81f4554f58637de01f4b8c782d2ac24fdb748a9d.jpg"},{"name":"WELL-PACED READER!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3118010/38930a0322a2ca21dbea634b68f12aff6c14fa49.jpg"},{"name":"GENEROUS AUDIENCE!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3118010/f20b66923947d17703cbfba3cb04042c439763f2.jpg"},{"name":"SURVIVOR!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3118010/049bb9da8b5bc3eb01913ed0f7b461a77b624b32.jpg"},{"name":"PIXELS AND NUMBERS!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3118010/6c84d407367b8c01526e7e78dab7ef55ade54cfc.jpg"},{"name":"SAVE ART!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3118010/8b7042da351d2a5b4add78c50dd52f257c4b8b7d.jpg"},{"name":"SAVE FILMS!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3118010/eb2ed09e0f69ac23570a3bbac656995d0217d049.jpg"},{"name":"BROKEN RIBS!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3118010/d26ca64efc2830c247e4ba18cc82a59787f9228c.jpg"},{"name":"BRAIN SHOWER!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3118010/932ff7623299cce86bd11651e9c0df09e1784f3d.jpg"},{"name":"FOLDING CHAIR!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com